.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ccea83edf89cac9c10f584c38d943a63731c3a","tid":207483,"uid":45028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:04:21.000Z","msg":"用2000億買到disney甘我刀買喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81bd88bde21d2ceda26110fa52778590434a3ff","tid":207483,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:44:56.000Z","msg":"搞錯，以為中資添"}]}